data.title: If Ottomans/Turks have won the first Balkan War, can they expel Bulgarians, Greeks, Serbs, etc. like Armenians during the Great War?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 3): Nice to see an acknowledgement of the nascent genocidal tendencies of the Young Turks.
